  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `Geth/v1.8.6-patched-leveldb-8818ab0b/linux-amd64/go1.9.2`\r\nOS & Version: unknown\r\nCommit hash : unknown\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nWhen requesting **state at a future block** (block height above the current block), **an error is returned**. Alternatively, `null` is returned.\r\n\r\n##### requesting state at future block\r\nHere is the **parity** response for **state at future block**\r\n```\r\ncurl  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x04cb1ade2bd72acd758d4f7abacbc633fc532857\",\"0xffffff\"],\"id\":73}' https://pmainnet.infura.io/\r\n\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"error\":{\"code\":-32602,\"message\":\"Unknown block number\"},\"id\":73}\r\n```\r\n\r\n##### requesting future block\r\nHere is the **geth** response for a **future block**\r\n```\r\ncurl  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBlockByNumber\",\"params\":[\"0xffffff\", false],\"id\":73}' https://gmainnet.infura.io/\r\n\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":73,\"result\":null}\r\n```\r\n\r\nHere is the **parity** response for a **future block**\r\n```\r\ncurl  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBlockByNumber\",\"params\":[\"0xffffff\", false],\"id\":73}' https://pmainnet.infura.io/\r\n\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"result\":null,\"id\":73}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nWhen requesting state at a future block (block height above the current block), a string with `<nil>` is returned.\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x04cb1ade2bd72acd758d4f7abacbc633fc532857\",\"0xffffff\"],\"id\":73}' https://gmainnet.infura.io/\r\n\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":73,\"result\":\"\\u003cnil\\u003e\"}\r\n```\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nsee above `curl` invocations\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\nn/a",
